summary.name: KitchenAid Electrics
summary.description: What a bright idea! KitchenAid presents a collection of appliances that will help you add a little color to your kitchen. With a style all their own, each piece features accents of vibrant color and sturdy, durable construction. Add to that KitchenAid's reputation for unsurpassed performance and quality and you're assured the best tools no matter what your culinary endeavor. 1-year hassle-free replacement warranty.

summary.name: KitchenAid KSC700 Slow Cooker
summary.description: Great food takes time? something you just don't have. KitchenAid's patient slow cooker does most of the work for you, gently heating the most tender roasts and sumptuous stews you've ever tasted. Just fill the 7-quart ceramic pot with your favorite ingredients, program the 10-hour timer with digital display and let the 400-watt heating element slowly simmer your meal to perfection. The 5-setting cook and serve control keeps food warm until it's ready to serve. 1-year hassle-free replacement warranty. Model KSC700.
bullets: Includes glass lid with large handle and soft seal
Electronic temperature management system
Food temperature alert

summary.name: KitchenAid KSM150PS Stand Mixer, 5 Qt. Artisan
summary.description: Retro styled and easy to use, the KitchenAid Artisan stand mixer is the perfect kitchen companion. Employing a unique tilting head to facilitate bowl and content removal, this mixer is undeniably handy. 1-year hassle-free replacement warranty. Model KSM150PS.
